 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Protection from Evil
@60023 = ~Wand of Protection from Evil~
@60024 = ~When activated, the wand creates a magical barrier around the recipient at a distance of one foot. The barrier moves with the recipient and has two major effects: First, all attacks made by evil or evilly enchanted creatures against the protected creature receive a penalty of -2 to each attack roll. Second, summoned demons cannot target the protected creature.

