//Chill Touch
@60029 = ~Wand of Chill Touch~
@60030 = ~When activated, a blue glow encompasses the wielder's hand, and <PRO_HESHE> uses this energy to attack the life force of an adjacent creature. No attack roll is needed. The touched creature takes 5d4 magic cold damage and must save or lose 3 points of Strength for 5 rounds. The Strength loss is cumulative; if the creature is reduced to 0 Strength, it dies instantly.

An undead creature suffers no damage or Strength loss, but will be affected by panic for 2 turns unless it successfully makes a Save vs. Wand.

STATISTICS:
(Necromancy)

Charge abilities:
– Chill Touch
