    – 5d4 magic cold damage
    – Lose 3 points of Strength for 5 rounds
  – Undead:
    – Suffer panic for 2 turns
  Range: Touch
  Area of Effect: 15-ft. radius
  Duration: Special
  Saving Throw:
  – Save vs. Death negates strength damage
  – Save vs. Wand negates panic (if undead)

