//Blur
@60100 = ~Wand of Blur~
@60100 = ~When activated, the outline of the wielder's form becomes blurred, shifting and wavering. This distortion causes all missile and melee attacks against the wielder to be made with a -3 penalty. The wielder also gains a +1 bonus to all of <PRO_HISHER> Saving Throws.

STATISTICS:
(Illusion/Phantasm)

Charge abilities:
– Blur
  – Attacks against wielder are made at a -3 penalty
  – +1 bonus to all saving throws
  Area of Effect: Self
  Duration: %duration%
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~
